{"featured_counts":0,"common_counts":12,"collapsed_counts":0,"reviewing_counts":0,"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":true,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/560858738/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=1\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/560858738/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=0\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","totals":2},"data":[{"id":566371814,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/566371814","content":"因为题主说“每个人都有自己的思维，也不一定要用到多高深的数学知识才能证明”。您觉得这句话是不是对过去几百年间数学家们对这个问题的工作的践踏和亵渎？数不尽的聪明人把初级数论变换各种姿势试图证明哥猜都失败了，哥猜已经被证明根本不是基础知识能解决的了。\u003cbr\u003e而题主那句话仿佛在说，“简单的方法就可以证，我想到了，前面几百年都没人能想到哦~”任何一个知道哥猜难度，对前人工作和科学精神怀有敬畏之心的人，看到都会生气的。我觉得这种态度也是这个问题下面大家开嘲讽的原因。\u003cbr\u003e嗨呀真的好气哦！","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1545896042,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"54bfd7a12f524a02a8eb6b9b04b510b9","url_token":"dai-dai-34-78","name":"黛黛","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f2d8c7ce2bc83df3ed5a35a0232b6cf5_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f2d8c7ce2bc83df3ed5a35a0232b6cf5_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/54bfd7a12f524a02a8eb6b9b04b510b9","user_type":"people","headline":"实验室宅女。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":1,"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0,"child_comment_count":3,"child_comments":[{"id":566374425,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/566374425","content":"我对数学方面不曾有太多理解，但是试想：文学批判这件事（各种角度各种层面各种思想的文学评论解读经典文章），难道也是对过去几百年的文学家的创作的践踏与亵渎？\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e所以哎呀，我就是很期待历史性的时刻。（就算不成，也是及时切断数学界的一条不正确路）","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1545896357,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"author","member":{"id":"0ec085f233af039fe8a0cd0ea376e48c","url_token":"gai-gai-gai-gai-gai-2","name":"铮铮铮铮铮","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/989ab4f722c3d80c6938c563fbfccf20_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/989ab4f722c3d80c6938c563fbfccf20_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/0ec085f233af039fe8a0cd0ea376e48c","user_type":"people","headline":"俄语俄语书法小生","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":0,"reply_to_author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"54bfd7a12f524a02a8eb6b9b04b510b9","url_token":"dai-dai-34-78","name":"黛黛","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f2d8c7ce2bc83df3ed5a35a0232b6cf5_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f2d8c7ce2bc83df3ed5a35a0232b6cf5_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/54bfd7a12f524a02a8eb6b9b04b510b9","user_type":"people","headline":"实验室宅女。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false}},"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0},{"id":566379980,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/566379980","content":"\u003cp\u003e我就知道您是个文科生……理科生听到那句话大概率会生气的，唉。文无第一没有标准，一千个读者眼里有一千个哈姆雷特，文学艺术历史里确实是可以有不同的观点，你这个观点我那个观点，很多时候可以没有对错。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是理科科学里一就是一，二就是二，有一个标准！有一个对错！前人证肯定也是从初级方法开始证起，这是一个循序渐进的过程。现在公认要用更高等，更复杂的数学工具。那就只有掌握这些数学工具，对前人工作有阅读能力的前提下，不管最后证对证错，才有资格有能力开口说“证明”这两个字！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e轻飘飘地开口说“其实可以不用这么高深的数学知识”就是对前人工作的侮辱和践踏，也是一种不掌握高等工具就妄想一步登天的怠惰和傲慢。\u003c/p\u003e","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_dele